reviewText: He is THE funniest guy!! Live his stuff!
Best comedian ever- you will definately not be dissapointed and if you are his comedy is probably about people like you
R.I.P Ollie you were great!!! Great Dvd you could tell that it was made in the 80's. Funny as Hell!!
Great memories of the late Ollie Joe Prater. You will laugh!! Definitely worth the money. A true legend gone too soon
